cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this work, please cite it as below. Authorship note (human direction, AI implementation) is in DISCLOSURES.md."
title: "memory-organ: base-agnostic long-term memory for frozen LLMs"
abstract: >-
  A research preview of a mechanism for attaching a long-term associative memory to a frozen LLM and
  transferring that same frozen memory to a different frozen base via a small learned translator.
type: software
